title: Where Have You Gone
lyrics: I look around, alone Where have you gone? You haven't told me anything, So I ask you, where have you gone? I've look around, alone Where have you gone? You haven't told me anything, So I ask you, where have you gone? Where have you gone? So tell me where have you gone? Where have you gone? So tell me where where have you gone? The night is here Where is the light that shines on me right now So I ask you, where have you gone? Where have you gone? So tell me where where have you gone?
